# {{projectName}}

DARE-shaped Laravel 11 API. Layered Design: Controller → Service → Repository → Model.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
composer install
php artisan key:generate
docker compose up -d postgres
php artisan migrate --seed
php artisan l5-swagger:generate
php artisan serve
```

## Commands

- `php artisan serve` — dev server (port 8000)
- `php artisan pail` — tail formatted logs
- `pest` (or `php artisan test`) — run tests
- `vendor/bin/phpstan analyse` — static analysis
- `composer audit` — dependency audit
- `php artisan l5-swagger:generate` — regenerate OpenAPI from annotations
- `php artisan reverb:start` — WebSocket server (port 8080 by default)

## Endpoints

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | none | Exchange email+password for Sanctum token |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Bearer | Current user info |
| GET | `/api/users` | Bearer | List users (query: page, limit) |
| POST | `/api/users` | Bearer (admin) | Create user |
| GET | `/openapi.json` | none | OpenAPI 3.x document |
| GET | `/api/documentation` | none | Swagger UI |

## Layered Design

- `app/Http/Controllers/Api/` — HTTP layer
- `app/Http/Requests/` — FormRequest validation
- `app/Services/` — business logic
- `app/Repositories/` — Eloquent queries (controllers/services never touch the model directly)
- `app/Models/` — Eloquent
- `app/Llm/` — Provider abstraction (`Contracts/LlmProvider` + `Providers/{Dummy,OpenAi}`)

